<p><strong>The recuerd0 CLI — your terminal, your memories</strong></p>

<p>Everything in the web UI, available from your terminal. Install with one command:</p>

<pre style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: 14px; overflow-x: auto;">brew install recuerd0/tap/recuerd0</pre>

<p>Or download directly from the <a href="https://github.com/maquina-app/recuerd0-cli/releases">releases page</a>.</p>

<p><strong>Quick example:</strong></p>

<pre style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: 14px; overflow-x: auto;"># Set your API token
export RECUERD0_TOKEN="your-token-here"
export RECUERD0_HOST="<%= root_url.chomp("/") %>"

# List your workspaces
recuerd0 workspace list --pretty

# Search across everything
recuerd0 search "deployment config" --pretty</pre>

<p>The CLI supports everything — workspaces, memories, search, versioning — all from the command line.</p>

<p style="margin: 24px 0;">
